=====
bleak
=====

.. figure:: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hbldh/bleak/master/Bleak_logo.png
    :target: https://github.com/hbldh/bleak
    :alt: Bleak Logo
    :scale: 50%


.. image:: https://github.com/hbldh/bleak/workflows/Build%20and%20Test/badge.svg
